data.description: Welcome to a 4-bedroom, 2-full bath home blistering with historic charm. Original hardwood floors, stone fireplace and woodwork. The spacious first floor layout presents flexibility for multiple living spaces, bedrooms, or offices. The home posses the ability to be set up as a multi family dwelling as well. With multiple entrances and the upstairs kitchenette. The second floor also offers three bedrooms and a full bathroom. The seller is providing a home warranty with HSA Home Warranty for added peace of mind. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this home! Seller is selling in AS IS condition.
